{"tid":823651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路況惡劣巴士停駛鐵路受限　打工仔鬧爆：點返工呀！","createTime":"2018-09-17T00:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T01:34:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e0e538026a518013b65c8a6cedd4a7a83e1f53dd","tid":823651,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:16:40.000Z","msg":"經過「怪物級」超強颱風山竹洗禮，港九各區到處滿目瘡痍，多條主要馬路、幹線佈滿被強風吹倒的大樹、垃圾等，無奈政府並未帶頭讓公務員放假，今日只停課、不停工，廣大打工仔今晨仍要趕上班。<br />\n<br />\n九巴、新巴及城巴除少部份路線外，大部份日間路線仍因路面情況惡劣而要暫停服務，加上東鐵綫只能維持有限度服務，令上班一族感徬徨，紛紛在網上訴苦「點返工呀！<br />\n」<br />\n早上7時許，大批新界居民抵達大圍站，始發現無列車出九龍，月台逼滿等車乘客，也有人指接駁巴士站已有近千乘客在候車；港鐵大埔墟站實施人流管制，即使往紅磡站方向維持有限度服務，但據港鐵職員指，月台位置因有大量乘客，故乘客需在未准入閘，需在閘機外等候港鐵職員安排；暫未知重開入閘時間。而東鐵綫來往大埔墟站至羅湖站方向列車服務暫停。<br />\n<br />\n多區馬路仍然受阻，將軍澳有多處塌樹橫亘路中仍未清理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180917/large/1537141469_ffd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180917%2Flarge%2F1537141469_ffd9.jpg&h=fb47bd88&s={SIZE}\" />大大埔墟港鐵站外逼滿趕返工市民。鄧溢禧攝(蘋果日報)"},{"pid":"e51c5d1b606458178db9179808c827c3351c53fe","tid":823651,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180917/large/1537141469_0518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180917%2Flarge%2F1537141469_0518.jpg&h=cd009303&s={SIZE}\" />車站貼出告示，表明由於受塌樹和障礙物影響，東鐵綫列車服務受阻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180917/large/1537141469_274c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180917%2Flarge%2F1537141469_274c.jpg&h=d3425020&s={SIZE}\" />港鐵在其網頁上載的列車受阻詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180917/large/1537141682_f5e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180917%2Flarge%2F1537141682_f5e3.jpg&h=ab0bd3fa&s={SIZE}\" />大圍站出九龍月台逼滿候車市民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180917/large/1537141682_36c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180917%2Flarge%2F1537141682_36c8.jpg&h=67a57c43&s={SIZE}\" />將軍澳多處仍有塌樹未清理。"},{"pid":"1dbc869b97faadfd948e8b6323ec6424fe2c6011","tid":823651,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:18:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180917/58690343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F58690343&d=di6OOXBpnfi%2F92gnHlkrhf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=da627e90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F58690343&h=48dce31b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180917/58690343</a>"},{"pid":"e54744485c2d7359ece75061e5616247937c1ee7","tid":823651,"uid":77196,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:18:45.000Z","msg":"所有高官仆街死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b1ee45ac55700a84f89f131c8c2fa5c5c17c37","tid":823651,"uid":27664,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/081949_1201d053835946d1c6b83a72e6c9bd86.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F081949_1201d053835946d1c6b83a72e6c9bd86.png&h=10aa9c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/081951_6f45efe012b938dcae0dcb52a6b9b8c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload